title: 1964–65 Rangers F.C. season
text:
The 1964–65 season is the 85th season of competitive <a href="Association%20football">football</a> by <a href="Rangers%20F.C.">Rangers</a>.
Overview.
Rangers played a total of 54 competitive matches during the 1964–65 season.
Results.
All results are written with Rangers' score first.
